4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for individuals without prior knowledge to become cybersecurity specialists. The program lasts 16 weeks and includes three live online classes per week, with a maximum of 16 participants per class. Students will gain foundational skills in Windows, Linux, network, and server administration, and will learn about cloud security, penetration testing, cyber threat intelligence, and compliance with international standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. Graduates receive an official completion certificate recognized by multiple institutions. Classes are available in English or Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity). stop